# STOP. READ THIS BEFORE ANY GIT OPERATION.

## DO NOT COMMIT. DO NOT PUSH.

NOT after finishing an article.
NOT after fixing a bug.
NOT after fixing a typo.
NOT after any file edit.
NOT "while you're at it".
NOT because it "makes sense".
NOT because the work is done.

## THE ONLY TIME YOU MAY COMMIT OR PUSH:

The user has typed one of these exact words in their message:
- коммить / коммит / commit
- пуш / пушь / push
- закоммить / запушь

